title: 2014-15 patch (v0.5) for FIFA 11
description:
2014-15 patch (v0.5) for FIFA 11


included:

- FIFA 11 Selector
* New: tournament graphics: change to (Champions league, EL, WC, ...) graphics (= linked adboards, kits, shoes, stadiums, ... will appear ingame)
* New: boot assignments - 3D (-render) preview of boots
* New: boot assignments - assign boots for a specific tournament to players (CL, EL, WC, ...)
* New: Arena Stadium - added "Random stadium" : let game chose the Arena Stadium randomly
* Arena Ball - List updated + 3D (-render) preview added
* fix: player assignments - errors
* improvements
* removed: English commentary

- db
* date 17.10.2014 
* Online & Offline version
* improvement: more realistic player behaviours (--> xtra (unknown) player traits added)
* New league: Turkish liga
* New promoted teams
* career: added turkish league, cup, supercup (+ CL/EL tickets)
* career: update supercup teams
* career: update CL/EL final stadium

- kits
* all 2014-15 kits (FIFA 15 + improvements)
* classic kits (from fifa 15)
* xtra GK kits (random chosen at each match)
* Champions league kits (+ correct numbers/fonts)
* update referee kits: english leagues, CL, EL

Installation:
1. install fifa 11 
2. install ea patch (1.01)

3. install 2014-15 patch (v0.5) for FIFA 11
* run installer "2014-15 patch (v0.5) for FIFA 11 (part 1).exe"
* run installer "2014-15 patch (v0.5) for FIFA 11 (part 2).exe"


Notes
- Selector dont start up (if u have .net 2.0) : copy included "Selector (.NET 2.0 version)" folder content to FIFA 11 folder


Problems:
- crashes, ...: use the "i68 regenerator" (select "take care of edited files..." > go , can take some time)
